    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;New MIB objects, tcpIpxConnTable, udpIpxTable, tcpUnspecConnTable and udpUnspecTable are presented in this paper, to be used in place of tcpConnTable and udpListenerTable when TCP and UDP are running over IPX.  This document defines an Experimental Protocol for the Internet community.  This does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
